I"E<p>在<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Typora</code>中设置 Image 的路径：</p>

<p><img src="/img/md-post/2022-02-10-Typora%20image/Screen%20Shot%202022-02-10%20at%2006.45.22.png" alt="Screen Shot 2022-02-10 at 06.45.22" /></p>

<p><img src="/img/md-post/2022-02-10-Typora%20image/Screen%20Shot%202022-02-10%20at%2006.46.19.png" alt="Screen Shot 2022-02-10 at 06.46.19" /></p>

<p>此后在<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Typora</code>中插入图片后，图片的位置会自动保存在<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">../img/md-post/${filename}</code>，这里是指去上一个目录找<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">img/md-post</code>文件夹，<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">${filename}</code>是图片的文件名。</p>

<p>而后，在写<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">markdown</code>的时候，将<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">typora-root-url</code>的路径设置为<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">../</code>,如下所示：</p>

